casebody.data:
Eichner, Respondent, v. Liverpool & London & Globe Ins. Co., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 17, 1890.) Appeal from fourth district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Butler, Stillman & Hubbard, for appellant. H. Joseph, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. See 8 N. Y. Supp. 948.
